parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Unintended Electrical System Activation and Fire
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The unintended activation of the horn and windshield wipers, followed by a vehicle fire, can cause damage to the vehicle, injury to occupants, and potentially lead to fatalities.
symptoms: the windshield wipers move on their own
flames appear from the dashboard or door area.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The engine stalling while driving can cause a loss of power, leading to a loss of control, and potentially resulting in accidents or injuries.
symptoms: The vehicle stalls while driving at any speed
the engine shuts off without warning
the vehicle is unable to maintain speed.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Seat Belt Buckle Failure Due to Plastic Retainer Deterioration
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the seat belt buckle can lead to a loss of restraint in the event of a crash, increasing the risk of injury or fatality.
symptoms: The seat belt buckle fails to latch or unlatch
the seat belt buckle is loose or wobbly
the seat belt webbing is not securely held in place
the seat belt warning light is illuminated.
